[#ftl]]
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html>
<head>
	<meta charset="UTF-8">
	<title>会员注册第二步--验证注册邮箱，成功的返回页</title>
	<meta name="Keywords" content="会员中心，会员注册第二步，验证注册邮箱" />
	<meta name="Description" content="会员中心，会员注册第二步，验证注册邮箱" />
	<link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="${basecss}/css/default/register.css">
	<script>
		$(function() {
			$(".changemail").click(function(){
				$(".changebox").toggle();
			});
		});
	</script>
</head>
<body>
		<div class="container">
			<div class="main">
				<div class="topcommon">
					<img src="${baseimg}/imgs/default/findpw01.png" alt="" />
					<h2>从这里，找到更好的自己！</h2>
				</div>
				<div class="midcommon">
					<div class="logotop">
						<img src="${baseimg}/imgs/default/login_logo.png" alt="" />
						会员注册
					</div>
					<div class="registercontainer">
						<div class="steps">
							<div class="stepitem curstepitem">
								<span class="rectbg">1</span>
								<span>填写账户信息</span>
							</div>
							<div class="linebg redlinebg"></div>
							<div class="stepitem curstepitem">
								<span class="rectbg">2</span>
								<span>验证注册邮箱</span>
							</div>
							<div class="linebg"></div>
							<div class="stepitem">
								<span class="rectbg">3</span>
								<span>基本信息</span>
							</div>
							<div class="linebg"></div>
							<div class="stepitem">
								<span class="rectbg">4</span>
								<span>支付会员费</span>
							</div>
						</div>
						<div class="registercontmiddle">
						[#if err.err_register_verify??]
        	              <div class="goemail">
								<div class="mailtip">
									<img src="${baseimg}/imgs/default/waring.png" alt="" />
									对不起，该用户不存在，无法激活！
								</div>
							</div>
                        [#elseif err.err_timeout]
                       <div class="goemail">
								<div class="mailtip">
									<img src="${baseimg}/imgs/default/waring.png" alt="" />
									对不起，此邮件已被激活，请不要重复激活！
								</div>
							</div>
        	           [#else]
							<div class="goemail">
								<div class="mailtip">
									<img src="${baseimg}/imgs/default/yes.png" alt="" />
									邮箱认证成功！
									<p>完善您的个人信息并缴纳学费，即可成为超天才正式会员！</p>
								</div>
								<a href="${base}/register_improve/${user.uid}" class="toemail submit">下一步</a>
							</div>
							<div class="moretest">
								<h2>成为正式会员，您将享受到以下服务：</h2>
								<ul class="questionlist">
									<li>1.注册的账号可以畅行超天才产品，如天财评论、并购平台、职业经理人培训......</li>
									<li>2.获得职业经理人学员申请资格</li>
									<li>3.在人间仙境体验全部社交功能，与企业大咖直接交流</li>
								</ul>
								
							</div>
					   [/#if]
						</div>
					</div>
				</div>
			</div>
	</div>
</body>
</html>
